{"tid":137916,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普轟頒錯獎源於「太政治」","createTime":"2017-02-28T07:54:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-28T08:14:30.000Z","uid":25556,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5f2b7774858dadcad7592d2bb2f6219f54b21b74","tid":137916,"uid":25556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T07:54:36.000Z","msg":"第89屆奧斯卡頒獎禮發生罕見「意外」，《雌雄大盜》男女主角華倫比堤（Warren Beatty）及菲丹娜惠（Faye Dunaway）誤把最佳電影《月亮喜歡藍》的獎座頒錯予《星聲夢裡人》，成為國際笑話。<br />\n<br />\n由於在頒獎禮上，司儀Jimmy Kimmel多次嘲笑美國總統特朗普，後者一直沉默，未有透過Twitter回應，直至「擺烏龍」事件壓軸上演，他終於把握時機，趁傳媒訪問他即發炮：「我覺得他們太過專注於政治，才會衰收尾。」又說自己亦曾出席過奧斯卡，相比現在明顯較失色，令人感到「傷感」云云。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170228/s00007/1488266196627#sthash.jFTLk041.dpuf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170228%2Fs00007%2F1488266196627%23sthash.jFTLk041.dpuf&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4Zyy%2FjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=aec300f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170228%2Fs00007%2F1488266196627%23sthash.jFTLk041.dpuf&h=efea6214\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170228/s00007/1488266196627#sthash.jFTLk041.dpuf</a>"},{"pid":"790c2e14506d15a8e7a1ef08a64a8b24cedceaa8","tid":137916,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T07:58:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f1fb1f5344a5e7a7d214b145c546e553a934706","tid":137916,"uid":40842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T08:00:15.000Z","msg":"侵侵又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da032f4b52550c1c6ca16b352dd837af2863f3cf","tid":137916,"uid":25556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited